升至 15 分鐘，等同翻兩倍，且計費費率因測試項目增加跟著提升，將進一步挹注未來營運。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\n\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;觀察目前手機陣營，僅蘋果旗艦級 iPhone 處理器採用 3 奈米製程，安卓陣營的兩大巨頭高通 (QCOM-US) 與聯發科 (2454-TW) 今年推出的 Snapdragon 8 gen 3 及天璣 9300 仍採用 4 奈米製程，明年也將推出採用 N3E 製程的旗艦晶片。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\n\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;另外，由於生成式 AI 趨勢成形，各家手機晶片業者也搭載新版 APU，用於運算數百億參數的大型語言模型 (LLM)，為因應客戶需求，測試廠也都規劃在今明年升級設備，因應客戶晶片複雜化的趨勢。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\n\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;展望明年，業界認為，明年在手機需求復甦，以及新技術加持下，手機晶片測試需求將重返成長，相關效應預期明年首季就可以陸續顯現。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n","hasCoverPhoto":1,"is24h":1,"isCategoryHeadline":1,"isIndex":1,"isOutsource":0,"keyword":["聯發科","高通","蘋果","3奈米","AI","生成式AI"],"newsId":5386632,"otherProduct":["TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON","TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON","TWS:6257:STOCK:COMMON","TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON","USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON"],"payment":0,"source":"","stock":["3711","2449","6257","2454","US-QCOM"],"summary":"隨著手機晶片陸續導入 3 奈米製程，加上業者為滿足 AI 運算需求，在既有核心架構上再搭載性能強大的獨立 APU，帶動整體測試時間翻倍，也推升每小時費率 (Hourly rate)，IC 封測廠日月光投控 (3711-TW)、京元電 (2","title":"手機晶片測試時長翻倍 IC測試廠啖商機","video":"","publishAt":1700390641,"coverSrc":{"xs":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386632/xs/3b24e6764d3309fd86c7ec90689678aa.jpg","width":100,"height":56},"s":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386632/s/3b24e6764d3309fd86c7ec90689678aa.jpg","width":180,"height":101},"m":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386632/m/3b24e6764d3309fd86c7ec90689678aa.jpg","width":380,"height":214},"l":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386632/l/3b24e6764d3309fd86c7ec90689678aa.jpg","width":640,"height":360},"xl":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386632/xl/3b24e6764d3309fd86c7ec90689678aa.jpg","width":960,"height":540},"xxl":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386632/xxl/3b24e6764d3309fd86c7ec90689678aa.jpg","width":1080,"height":608}},"abTesting":null,"categoryId":827,"categoryName":"台股新聞","columnists":null,"magazine":null,"fundCategoryAbbr":[],"fbShare":0,"fbComment":0,"fbCommentPluginCount":0,"market":[{"code":"3711","name":"日月光投控","symbol":"TWS:371