3%。馬斯克和 X 平台拒絕對此爭議回文置評。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n","hasCoverPhoto":1,"is24h":0,"isCategoryHeadline":1,"isIndex":1,"isOutsource":0,"keyword":["X","推特","馬斯克","蘋果","迪士尼"],"newsId":5386387,"otherProduct":["USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON","USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON","USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON","USS:DIS:STOCK:COMMON","USS:WBD:STOCK:COMMON","USS:PARA:STOCK:COMMON","USS:CMCSA:STOCK:COMMON"],"payment":0,"source":null,"stock":["US-TSLA","US-AAPL","US-ORCL","US-DIS","US-LGF","US-WBD","US-PARA","US-CMCSA"],"summary":null,"title":"馬斯克挺反猶太言論引白宮譴責 特斯拉股東質疑聲起、X平台廣告遭撤","video":"","publishAt":1700285766,"coverSrc":{"xs":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386387/xs/22b718180591b80fe9faf1977590adc5.jpg","width":100,"height":56},"s":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386387/s/22b718180591b80fe9faf1977590adc5.jpg","width":180,"height":101},"m":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386387/m/22b718180591b80fe9faf1977590adc5.jpg","width":380,"height":213},"l":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386387/l/22b718180591b80fe9faf1977590adc5.jpg","width":640,"height":360},"xl":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386387/xl/22b718180591b80fe9faf1977590adc5.jpg","width":960,"height":539},"xxl":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386387/xxl/22b718180591b80fe9faf1977590adc5.jpg","width":1080,"height":607}},"abTesting":null,"categoryId":831,"categoryName":"美股雷達","columnists":null,"magazine":null,"fundCategoryAbbr":[{"name":"產業-科技","categoryAbbrId":"C37"}],"fbShare":0,"fbComment":0,"fbCommentPluginCount":0,"market":[{"code":"TSLA","name":"特斯拉","symbol":"USS:TSLA:STOCK"},{"code":"AAPL","name":"蘋果","symbol":"USS:AAPL:STOCK"},{"code":"ORCL","name":"甲骨文","symbol":"USS:ORCL:STOCK"},{"code":"DIS","name":"迪士尼","symbol":"USS:DIS:STOCK"},{"code":"WBD","name":"WRN BRS DS A O","symbol":"USS:WBD:STOCK"},{"code":"PARA","name":"Paramount Global Class B","symbol":"USS:PARA:STOCK"},{"code":"CMCSA","name":"康卡斯特公司","symbol":"USS:CMCSA:STOCK"}]},{"content":"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Wedbush 分析師周五 (17 日) 指出，科技股年底漲勢已經開跑。因此，在聯準會 (Fed) 擔憂消退之際，投資人應該準備準備好爆米花，觀賞這場邁向 2024 年的大戲，屆時科技業將加速準備重金投資雲端和人工智慧(\u0026nbsp;AI) 項目，「我們認為華爾街大大低估了這一點。」\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\n\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Wedbush 認為，雖然 2024 年 IT 預算預計僅小幅增長，但明年雲端和 AI 驅動的支出將增長 20% 至 25%，「企業和消費者領域的用例正爆炸式增長」。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\n\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;該華爾街券商也預測，根據最近的調查，科技業即將迎來「長期空頭回補」到年底，「因為成長型科技股的基本面堅如磐石」。「我們認為，新的科技牛市現已開始，隨著 AI 支出浪潮更廣泛席捲科技業，科技股已為 2024 年的強勁表現做好準備。」\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\n\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;此外，該券商分析報告指出，他們將 AI 視為「自 1995 年網路誕生以來最具變革性的技術趨勢」，並認為華爾街許多人低估了未來 10 年 AI 支出可能達 1 兆美元這一點。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\n\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;該報告形容這將是晶片和軟體產業大獲其利的時期，預期輝達 (NVDA-US) 和微軟 (MSFT-US) 將帶領這波趨勢。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\n\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Wedbush 列入喜愛名單的科技股包括：蘋果 (AAPL-US)、微軟、谷歌母公司 Alphabet (GOOGL-US)、Palo Alto Networks (PANW-US)、 Palantir (PLTR-US)、Zscaler (ZS-US)、CrowdStrike (CRWD-US)，以及 MongoDB (MDB-US)。\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n","hasCoverPhoto":1,"is24h":0,"isCategoryHeadline":1,"isIndex":1,"isOutsource":0,"keyword":["微軟","科技","AI","美股","產業","雲端"],"newsId":5386398,"otherProduct":["USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON","USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON","USS:CRWD:STOCK:COMMON","USS:ZS:STOCK:COMMON","USS:PLTR:STOCK:COMMON","USS:PANW:STOCK:COMMON","USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON","USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON","USS:MDB:STOCK:COMMON"],"payment":0,"source":null,"stock":["US-NVDA","US-MSFT","US-AAPL","US-GOOGL","US-PANW","US-PLTR","US-ZS","US-CRWD","US-MDB"],"summary":"Wedbush 分析師周五指出，科技股年底漲勢已經開跑。因此，在聯準會 (Fed) 擔憂消退之際，科技業將加速準備重金投資雲端和 AI 項目，「我們認為華爾街大大低估這一點。」","title":"科技股牛市已開跑！美券商：AI支出浪潮更廣泛 科技股將一路空頭回補至年底","video":"","publishAt":1700284008,"coverSrc":{"xs":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386398/xs/bb3d9b4b8b8de5e303ea16652e49502c.jpg","width":100,"height":56},"s":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386398/s/bb3d9b4b8b8de5e303ea16652e49502c.jpg","width":180,"height":101},"m":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386398/m/bb3d9b4b8b8de5e303ea16652e49502c.jpg","width":380,"height":214},"l":{"src":"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5386398/l/bb3d9b4b8b8de5e303ea16